{"tid":1799908,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"或會取代 Android? 全新操作系統 Facebook OS 即將推出","createTime":"2019-12-27T10:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T08:53:39.000Z","uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"68e800d946cae00a51725daf9b315bd55b345255","tid":1799908,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lu6Pxjx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLu6Pxjx.jpg&h=49e51720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了 Android 以及 iOS 系統，據說不久的將來會出現一個新的系統，而且更有望可以取替 Android。這個系統是由 Facebook 推出，目前細節尚未清楚，是否僅適用於智能手機 / 平板，抑或能否讓不同設備共用同一平台，目前亦是未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n根據傳聞，Facebook 已要求 Microsoft Windows NT 的合作者 Mark Lucovsky，為 Facebook 開發新的操作箹統，該系統將根據 The Information 的信息，從頭開始構建。但要記住一點，這裡說的是 Facebook 操作系統，而非 Facebook 應用，因此不要將兩者混淆。<br />\n<br />\n目前的 Android OS 以及 iOS，除了對 Facebook 的功能有所限制，同時亦存在安全和隱私問題。而透過 Facebook OS，Facebook 將可自由地改善及整合社交互動，同時安全和隱私部份將能處理得更好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2019/12/%E6%88%96%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3-android-%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-facebook-os-%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3-android-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2593%258D%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1-facebook-os-%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2587%25BA.html&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHZAcLRrMd6FPy3rP8eGE4os%3D&h=42da45c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2019/12/%E6%88%96%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3-android-%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-facebook-os-%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA.html</a>"},{"pid":"e59790b8415bb6b4296f4ee923583802964bf9b7","tid":1799908,"uid":7585,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:14:19.000Z","msg":